Function: atan2f
URL: https://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/7.1/com.qnx.doc.neutrino.lib_ref/topic/a/atan2.html
Synopsis: float atan2f( float y,
Headers: #include <math.h>
Parameters:
  - y, x: The value (y/x) for which you want to find the angle.
Examples:
Example 1:
#include <math.h>

double atan2( double y, 
              double x );

float atan2f( float y, 
              float x );

long double atan2l( long double y,
